  "longBusinessSummary": "Randoncorp S.A. manufactures and sells trailers and semi-trailers, and auto parts in Latin America and internationally. The company offers bodies, trailers, semi-trailers, and railcars; auto parts, including axles and suspensions to truck, bus, and implement manufacturers; truck, bus, trailer and semi-trailer brakes; commercial vehicle coupling components and systems; and hub and drum assemblies and cast steel brackets for the axles and suspensions of buses, trucks, trailers, farm machines, and tractors, as well as wheel end system solutions. It also provides financial solutions and services comprising financing, investments, consortium plans, insurance, and heavy vehicle leasing to transportation, logistics, agribusiness, and retail sectors. In addition, the company offers Frasle Mobility; Nanotechnology platform and solutions for advanced material transformation; and fleet management and technology solutions insurance companies, insurance brokers, transportation, and logistics sectors. Randoncorp S.A. was founded in 1949 and is headquartered in Caxias Do Sul, Brazil.",
